{"tid":1325051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721 悲觀預測","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T11:06:26.000Z","uid":263448,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff28d347da136060ce3d3995f31bf6ef00457703","tid":1325051,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"721，如果發生衝突，我好悲觀地認為，假如警方真係出動水炮車清場，我預測會咁：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「警方出動水炮車，有烈士上前硬食，死埋。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑，已經有5位以死明志，其他人為咗死得有價值，衝擊過立法會，連日遊行大小衝突，又倦又悲觀，警方再出布袋彈，甚至吹晒會出水炮車，唔擔保有人願意先過政府，成為衝突中既「第一條人命」。<br />\n<br />\n你知啦！水炮車威力咁大，射中頭係即死，只係得何君堯果班保皇黨同藍絲港豬就唔撚信咋！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>戴定頭盔先，我唔係鼓吹各位手足去「硬食水炮車」，我唔希望再有人命傷亡。</strong><br />\n<br />\n同時，我係放下狠話，螢幕前面既警察/高官，如果真係想係721出動水炮車，麻煩你掂量下，唔好迫得人太緊，又玩包圍。<br />\n狗急跳牆，一陣果邊真係有人做烈士比你殺死咗，呢邊示威者萬念俱灰，事旦全力衝一邊，你用防暴盾，佢地用重量拉盾等你失衡，人係好脆弱架！之後為咗個垃圾政府入浩園，我都唔想見到。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係我最壞既打算，麻煩雙方都退一步，唔好迫太緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31307f9b7fb948cc8f5da977fc0431d99180e589","tid":1325051,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"721 去遊行！721 去遊行！721 去遊行！"},{"pid":"5e976047d191b527647630ec69074352e2ec212a","tid":1325051,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496e2e7a6470748cbf2835510bb77875ba0e12ce","tid":1325051,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3ba1d535681fc6572f69ac4044495ba49d2a68","tid":1325051,"uid":265291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"加入再悲觀的話 如果中央唔理國際面子忍唔住出手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果差佬又出橡膠子彈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果堅持唔特赦義士呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9a3889a3d372efd42ec4cdbc43d87cf54de262","tid":1325051,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f65acc5b78193da488300de9c665225ad71a222","tid":1325051,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}